subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Alexandra Dulgheru, a Romanian qualifier ranked No. 201, won the Warsaw Open in her WTA Tour debut, beating Alona Bondarenko of Ukraine, 7-6 (3), 3-6, 6-0.
